<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   I think part of the problem with Beastmasters is the fact they want to be dish out a fair amount of melee damage, AND want their pets to be monsters too!<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
