Could be.  Could also be that part of the problem with magickions (I'm allowed to mangle YOUR class name, right? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   ) is that they don't actually pay attention to what *most* people are saying, and zoom in on the minority.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   Well know what? Ain't gonna happen... You, as Shadowknights, use your pet as a dot - your pet isn't supposed to be tanking for you.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
